                    Sporting a new beard at the Badminton Horse Trials.
                
            1977
                
                
            
            Image caption
                
                    Comedy duo Morecambe and Wise shared the stage with Prince Charles during their special Royal Charity Show in aid of the Queen's Jubilee Appeal.
                
            1978
                
                Image copyright
                 PA
                
            
            
