                    Taking to the water, Prince Charles windsurfing during Regatta Week at Cowes on the Isle of Wight.
                
            1979
                
                Image copyright
                 PA
                
            
            
            Image caption
                
                    In 1979, Prince Charles fulfilled an ambition to fly a pre-War Tiger Moth biplane, when he took to the skies over RAF Benson in Oxfordshire.
                
